description.narrative: New ElementAdolescent girls and boys have access to knowledge, skills and commodities to protect themselves from HIV, including easy access to HIV counselling and testing., which contributes to Hiv Prevention, Treatment And Care Of Children Living With Hiv. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Provide support in carrying out anthropological studies on the demand for health services in communities
